    df = df[df['income'] > 2000]
    df = df[df['job'].isin(['engineer', 'teacher', 'secretary'])]
    df = df.drop_duplicates(subset='city', keep='first')
    df = df[df['country'].isin(['Scotland', 'USA', 'France'])]
    return df
